headline: SNN Stock Might Rise Following FDA Nod for AETOS Stemless
summary: Smith & Nephew received FDA 510(k) clearance for a stemless anatomic total shoulder, AETOS Stemless. This represents a significant advancement in shoulder arthroplasty.
